#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.bitwise_and.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.bitwise\\_and"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitand.bitand:1 of
msgid "Compute the bit-wise AND of two tensors element-wise."
msgstr "按元素计算两个张量的按位与。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitand.bitand:3 of
msgid ""
"Computes the bit-wise AND of the underlying binary representation of the "
"integers in the input arrays. This ufunc implements the C/Python operator"
" ``&``."
msgstr ""
"计算输入数组中整数的二进制表示的按位与。此 ufunc 实现了 C/Python 的 ``&``"
" 操作符。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitand.bitand of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitand.bitand:7
#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitand.bitand:9 of
msgid "Only integer and boolean types are handled."
msgstr "仅处理整数和布尔类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitand.bitand:11 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了该参数，则其形状必须可以广播到输入形状。"
"如果未提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）"
"的长度必须等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitand.bitand:16 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitand.bitand of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitand.bitand:21 of
msgid "**out** -- Result."
msgstr "**out** -- 结果。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitand.bitand of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitand.bitand:24 of
msgid ":py:obj:`logical_and`, :py:obj:`bitwise_or`, :py:obj:`bitwise_xor`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitand.bitand:27 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.bitand.bitand:28 of
msgid ""
"The number 13 is represented by ``00001101``.  Likewise, 17 is "
"represented by ``00010001``.  The bit-wise AND of 13 and 17 is therefore "
"``000000001``, or 1:"
msgstr ""
"数字 13 用 ``00001101`` 表示，同样，17 用 ``00010001`` 表示。13 和 17 的"
"按位与结果是 ``000000001``，即 1："

